title: High concentrations reported at 7:00, 05/19/2016
body: __Update for May 19, 2016 at 08:46 CST.__ There are 2 monitoring sites reporting a 1-hr AQI above 85. The maximum 1-hr AQI of 93 (PM2.5) was reported at Clinton, Rainbow Par [AQS ID: 190450021] by the **Iowa DNR**. Learn more at AQI Watch.
